settings.description: Pulley Platforms react to the Mario Bros.'s weight. Always keep an eye on both platforms at the same time and make sure you have the room you need to jump!
Roto-discs are like Fire Bars, but with much more room to dodge! Just make sure to keep your wits about you; they're a lot faster, too!
A quick level that focuses on rotating platforms. Keep your eye out for any Advance Coins you come in contact with along the way!
